[recv] {"type": "turn_end", "message": {"role": "assistant", "content": [{"type": "thinking", "thinking": "**Evaluating classloader behavior**\n\nI’m thinking about how the validator factory uses the returned class and whether that feels too fake. It’s interesting that it uses a custom classloader that only loads known classes already in the image, using an alias and not relying on runtime class definitions. But is this unsupported? I wonder if the public API necessitates a matching class name with FQCN since the ClassLoader API does. If it works, it might violate the spec, which reviewers could reject. I need to consider what’s naturally supported.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_027378da18c5b346016a3bfb0890d88194ae2cf628c4a11cfa\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"content\":[],\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABqO_svlSzwpggh-mF2MGixvGPgcdckdFDjene4-mlEtl8iOimUv8KZcqf0LMJgi1qiSX-8Ve6bj2jNjF_rKdL2Y6tgvrKou8xjwgNO2vRtaQWMA9ZkbzYn_dzYnoMb9pOULjwnHfEwgHAl4Vl4NmH0seBXjv5RIdjKBsb5Ucu6nMSq-AbcAdFpEDey67QRsgoxWWTA8BBU8Sk0GhRTGqT6l4WtQzGV1FocCWTvvEfb6kuXyhVb8569Dbii8a0dMOQdb9TxkF_rpAKQX6e6F7s4GTm8l0CZ8yhcTcAEJXM1ni-6t1jcgWCNzwwgrgLSwxJbFnWwxtw1Xtjmbt_pGZzRwxp9aKoYq-GbTDckhECauY_1_cRt07Mpz4L69u0J7juuJ54OUfvMwYT1rKdVe6MBGfT-dVWf4K9MGmAEE64IHBVguuJQ60I7Q3WroEQtSaSlAu8wh9IsS3PpyqseeJMibEwraKz0f1mHSLya3uEg9iombRHYnvS6GQ4D2FgTctcyESeTPt7WYasvnVSzoV9ZvR7cAekv3INzmCWScwcZksP-Ib-JE3xH977045FzX6IEMrDk6qlC-fvQVD9EVkXoZMuGfp6BERmflJU7IoNk4CJHG0jP0-RyAdT8mISoplNSyduYIWLi7xevW6kkvZSxn54-HfLV8QraD55y0keyas9s3zpASY09RhrdKs8RLuUdS6-1N-vQsDlfmDNzPlB0JGB8LHf8yySiBk0z7cNZh1DXyG7GqYrQNCevdTORZqh_tf5uGg57N2xeFA4U0jQKOvbdcP7O8Mrse743CiXe3PS8txSdj5C1M-U8nTu8kgXzeaNCcRCA8OBQiIWf0Cuw2aXRM4xY5SIc4uhdn1s3Jk69Bqr8CBbNN8owIXWTZylcw38V4EEW_JvCKnVG5c-YclSSfjZ_ZSk7J4rGCoBnlB7kOaGNlkOGPaQYU331nhUUHcG7WvOug1R2YWzBpcKe7bOcl4IZ-RulfXGNHGcme0Y28K221a1d7A2tSbuSByVVH3ZpAIsO1KRfkxTk_uLMPSSPP0LrNez8YBKFZIZqH1QD2u6rqtt12h8XEE0-Yte3199oSnfZSINGC2d_Gv5tRw_8ey__mIBoNAgGogeuzsT97H7ingbjmJ7upCGoTfyRWAPeMORp3YuPaBDIPKlSk0amYMtyjq